  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized clinical trial assessing the outcome of two surgical strategies to treat
      severe obesity; laparoscopic gastric bypass and laparoscopic VBG. Main outcome is weight loss
      and weight loss maintenance but other factors as body composition, eating pattern, metabolic
      normalisation, energy expenditure will also be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
